# Bare name — NO `VITE_` prefix.
#
# `VITE_`-prefixed vars are inlined into `import.meta.env` and shipped to the
# browser bundle by Vite. This key must never reach the browser: it is read
# server-side only, in the Node process (`vite.config.ts` dev proxy via
# `loadEnv(mode, cwd, '')`, and the Vercel catch-all function in prod), which
# injects the `x-api-key` header on the outbound request to the API. The
# browser only ever calls same-origin `/api/*` with no key attached.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in a real value for
# local development.
API_KEY=
